WEBVTT

NOTE: Estimated from known TTS script; timing requires human review before Tier 1 captions.

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:08.512
If you need to sell your house fast in Janesville, Wisconsin, USA Home Buyers gives you a simple as-is cash-sale option.

2
00:00:08.512 --> 00:00:19.050
We buy homes throughout Janesville and Rock County, including Courthouse Hill, Old Fourth Ward, Rockport, Monterey, Downtown Janesville, and nearby working-class neighborhoods along the Rock River.

3
00:00:19.050 --> 00:00:24.319
This is for sellers who need certainty more than a long listing process.

4
00:00:24.319 --> 00:00:34.452
The property may be inherited, older, vacant, tenant-occupied, facing foreclosure pressure, or in need of repairs that do not make sense to complete before selling.

5
00:00:34.452 --> 00:00:41.747
You do not have to restore a historic home, clean everything out, or wait on a buyer's financing.

6
00:00:41.747 --> 00:00:44.247
The first step is easy.

7
00:00:44.247 --> 00:00:49.922
Tell us about the house, the condition, and the timeline that would help you.

8
00:00:49.922 --> 00:00:53.975
We review the property and provide a written cash offer.

9
00:00:53.975 --> 00:00:57.623
If the offer works, you choose the closing date.

10
00:00:57.623 --> 00:01:02.486
If you need extra time, we can work around that when possible.

11
00:01:02.486 --> 00:01:07.756
There is no commission, no required repair list, and no obligation to accept.

12
00:01:07.756 --> 00:01:14.241
We focus on making the next step clear so you can compare your options without pressure.

13
00:01:14.241 --> 00:01:20.320
For a straightforward cash offer on a Janesville-area home, call USA Home Buyers at 888-274-5006.

14
00:01:20.320 --> 00:01:23.900
We will explain the process and help you move forward.
